社推算，共和黨暫時在參議院的100席當中，拿到48席；民主黨暫時就有46席，兩黨都未取得過半數的優勢。<br />\n<br />\n至於眾議院的435席，民主黨暫時取得208席，共和黨暫時取得193席，亦未有政黨得票過半。"},{"pid":"55a985bdcedaf378388c138fc979a12b62a3dfbd","tid":2273874,"uid":12661,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"樓主標題寫得唔準確&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n佢話gaining in the House ，意思係眾議院內共和黨議席有所增加&hellip;但其實應該過唔到半數，所以稱唔上控制眾議院&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n不過都算係進步（而且出乎意料），兩年後國會再改選，就真係有機會控制參眾兩院喇&hellip;然後，等Pence、Pompeo （或者Ivanka)2024回朝啦！"},{"pid":"6314b24c51923f7853597be26fb0c9c8753823d6","tid":2273874,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4774df45ac61ae3299477f8b2517088a29fc0c0a","tid":2273874,"uid":82938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"de586dc2c8f81f7d294690fea08ee4dbf3a06a83","tid":2273874,"uid":308251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"70de75c38e6851a88473411fc7c02ccbf8daddd9","tid":2273874,"uid":355289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:44:00.000Z","msg":"現任232vs198<br />\n投緊就208vs193<br />\n都唔係穩過堆法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:56:32.000Z","msg":"共和黨已控制參議院"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:11:39.000Z","msg":"50對46+2<br />\n要1月GA次輪投票保多席先有51<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係50-50 harris就做tiebreaker玩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T06:45:43.000Z","msg":"Senate seats are up for election once every six years. There are 35 seats up for this year's Senate elections including special elections in Arizona and Georgia. The Democrats need to flip four seats to gain control. The Republicans need to retain at least 21 seats to keep control.<br />\n而家共和差3席"},{"pid":"f913ef745431db968dd4c7326a8e58629ee2a4d5","tid":2273874,"uid":201751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi